-06-28T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c25939b5ba07549a81322b99059abac0f52dccc","tid":1258753,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f48dd9b4186664214f288a7e7fa57c38ae82232","tid":1258753,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=4b6d2c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=87acecce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5b22a60b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=88b46c23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2de778b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=7528e0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=f8f04193\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"016ef903dc40681594e292e1ec2916177f304dcb","tid